{"tid":482020,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"坤 哥 為 脫 毒 狂 練 拳：要 瘦 過 吳 業 坤","createTime":"2017-11-27T18:00:29.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-28T03:57:58.000Z","uid":35964,"like":8,"dislike":133,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"551bb260f48aca30ffb7565e261d4f2bc2344eae","tid":482020,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:00:29.000Z","msg":"其實近年男星要「爆肌」已經是常識吧，連劇中與歐陽震華交換了靈魂的「偽毒」吳業坤（坤哥），都密密打拳操肌。日前（11月23日）坤哥在《誇世代》活動宣傳後就接着接受3個專訪，工作完成之後就急急腳離開。原來就是為了趕去做gym。點解做gym？坤哥就畀咗個好型嘅答案：「我想做返個男人！」<br />\n<br />\n細問之下，原來坤哥的意思是「男仔become男人」，覺得以前的自己太肥沒有男人味。其實坤哥加入娛樂圈已經7年時間。而現時27歲的他也說：「因為我都接近30，所以有呢個諗法。」坤哥表示，這個習慣已經堅持1年有多。「我嚟呢度做gym都差唔多1年，一星期都有2，3次。《超時空男臣》出街嗰時覺得自己好肥，所以先有打拳呢個念頭，想拍戲都好睇啲。」<br />\n<br />\n至於坤哥有否向《誇世代》的「大隻」型男陳豪、張繼聰、森美他們請教，坤哥就回答說：「冇㗎，我怕醜吖嘛。不過見到佢哋咁fit，我都會有動力。」睇相雖然坤哥未算練到六嚿腹肌的身形，不過對比起《超時空男臣》時已經有明顯分別。問到他的操肌目標，他就說：「我想瘦過吳業坤！」喂，吳業坤想瘦過吳業坤，即係點呢？好難明喎。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/images/1005800/xlarge/6edd8db56fa693888784eae2638a95ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F1005800%2Fxlarge%2F6edd8db56fa693888784eae2638a95ea.jpg&h=c49cbcf4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"874f516c395be2ad6c3b1ae86bed9069ccdc5f3e","tid":482020,"uid":117821,"like":143,"dislike":0,"score":143,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:02:13.000Z","msg":"收皮啦你老母"},{"pid":"2e1d6c59a411aa1924321bf9dcf3058bfbdab851","tid":482020,"uid":123456,"like":1,"dislike":16,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:04:31.000Z","msg":"好大隻好想比佢屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae21fe790ab279bee1a84ad857e926965316fb6f","tid":482020,"uid":17081,"like":74,"dislike":2,"score":72,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:33:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i/qh4toj.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi%2Fqh4toj.gif&h=cc195a58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2d9a5ba292475c2b4c331ff1330130da99a986e","tid":482020,"uid":87795,"like":83,"dislike":0,"score":83,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:50:14.000Z","msg":"呢條友真係好煩，好令人討厭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fbc93de833e7eee747bc9eaff5b593f2dd63478","tid":482020,"uid":41974,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T18:52:39.000Z","msg":"王組男 龜頭扑 偽毒坤"},{"pid":"5f0d275f62db09f71b7525a9dca9ba44a52a3476","tid":482020,"uid":24160,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-27T22:04:38.000Z","msg":"好樣衰<br />\n有肌肉又點<br />\n都係樣柒"},{"pid":"2578eb68a03d704a8561b54d5bdba02b2e9a306b","tid":482020,"uid":2547,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T00:15:03.000Z","msg":"擔心自己把頭髮先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到30會唔會甩到落天靈蓋<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64320a871af0133d3212f73bf9b7ff06a68efb26","tid":482020,"uid":53421,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T00:16:28.000Z","msg":"1拳打柒佢喇"},{"pid":"2a6e61ff86a30a84db0403c8e371096fbbb5841a","tid":482020,"uid":143572,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T00:25:33.000Z","msg":"Don&rsquo;t make stupid people famous"},{"pid":"c62dfbb74908698b24e0dc29b9f931837e5671a7","tid":482020,"uid":128921,"like":13,"dislike":3,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T00:38:34.000Z","msg":"已經大隻過好多連登仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a2d627f66c96e0980e88ef5364b20ea8c696ad","tid":482020,"uid":5253,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T00:42:36.000Z","msg":"做返棋喇好嗎"},{"pid":"bae7284c22a159ed495fe2a9f329228cef3dd683","tid":482020,"uid":91146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-28T01:16:24.000Z","msg":